text:
Thank you for your hard work. Thanks to everyone's
efforts, we were able to complete this job successfully.

Oh, yes...! Thank you so much for coming all the way here!
I'm so happy to have you here...!

You're an important colleague... Oh, your name...
You write those characters, I see. I'll remember thatâ™ª
Huh?! Oh, this pass!? I'm honored...!

You were talking to various staff members, huh?
I should be the one doing the greetings.

No, it's fine.
I just want to remember everyone.

We've crossed paths,
We were able to work together in this way.

so I wanted to cherish that...
and remember their names and personalities.

I hope we'll meet again someday,
and I'll properly greet them again.

I see...
I'm sure they won't forget about you either.
